28/06/2005
ANKARA, Turkey -- Prime Minister Recep Tayyip Erdogan is expected to visit the United States again on 5 July, according to an announcement Monday (27 June).
During the trip, Erdogan will attend a conference and deliver a speech on democracy, Islam and Turkey.
He will also meet managers of leading US companies.
Erdogan visited Washington in early June.
(NTV - 27/06/05)
